<body
    style="background:#F6F6F6; font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:12px; margin:0; padding:0;">
<h1>Dear {{var customer_name}}!</h1>

<p>On {{var quote.updated_at|formatDateTime:long}} you left a cart in our shop with the following content:</p>

<table width=100% border=1 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=5>
    <tr>
        <th>No</th>
        <th>Product</th>
        <th>SKU</th>
        <th>Qty</th>
        <th>Row Total</th>
    </tr>
    {{layout handle="onestepcheckout_abandonedcart_quote_item" order=$quote}}
    <tr>
        <th colspan=4 align=left>Rows total: {{var row_item_row_number}}</th>
        <th colspan=3>
            <table width=100% cellspacing=0 cellpadding="10" style="background-color:yellow">
                <tr>
                    <td align="left">Grand Total:</td>
                    <td align="right">{{var quote.grand_total|formatPrice}}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
    </tr>
</table>
<p>Please come back and take it here: <a href="{{var url_resume}}">Your cart link</a></p>
<br>
{{var related}}
<br>
<br>
<br>
<hr>
</body>